Package: python3-catnip
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 python3 (>= 3.13),
 python3-click,
Description: Catnip language - Python library and extensions
 Hybrid Rust/Python language with Tree-sitter parsing, pattern matching,
 broadcasting, non-deterministic recursion, and a bytecode VM with JIT.
 .
 This package contains the Python library, Rust extensions (_rs.so, _repl.so),
 MCP server, and dist-info metadata for plugin discovery.

Package: catnip
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 python3-catnip (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: Catnip language - CLI and standalone runner
 Hybrid Rust/Python language with Tree-sitter parsing, pattern matching,
 broadcasting, non-deterministic recursion, and a bytecode VM with JIT.
 .
 This package contains the catnip binary (Rust standalone runner),
 shell completions for bash/zsh/fish, and man pages.

Package: catnip-tools
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Catnip language - REPL and LSP server
 Interactive REPL (ratatui TUI) and Language Server Protocol server
 for the Catnip language.
 .
 Binaries: catnip-repl (interactive), catnip-lsp (LSP server).

